ryptocurrency or tainted bank money. You will want to turn that cash or cry=
pto into some more convenient and usable and legitimate-seeming=C2=A0form o=
f wealth: money in a clean bank account, most of all, but stocks and bonds =
and real estate and art can also work. The law is aware of this, and there =
are anti-money-laundering rules in most places that basically tell banks =
=E2=80=94=C2=A0but also crypto exchanges and stockbrokers and real estate a=
gents and art dealers =E2=80=94 =E2=80=9Cif someone comes to you with an en=
