<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The basic idea is that, if you are doing crime=
, you are probably getting paid in cash or in cryptocurrency or in, like, s=
omeone else=E2=80=99s bank account. If you do crime quite successfully, you=
 will have a lot of cash or cryptocurrency or tainted bank money. You will =
want to turn that cash or crypto into some more convenient and usable and l=
egitimate-seeming=C2=A0form of wealth: money in a clean bank account, most =
of all, but stocks and bonds and real estate and art can also work. The law=
 is aware of this, and there are anti-money-laundering rules in most places=
 that basically tell banks =E2=80=94=C2=A0but also crypto exchanges and sto=
ckbrokers and real estate agents and <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloomberg=
business.com/click/32923785.285424/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdz=
L25ld3NsZXR0ZXJzLzIwMjEtMDYtMjEvbW9uZXktc3R1ZmYtbG9yZHN0b3duLWV4ZWN1dGl2ZXM=
taGFkLWdvb2QtdGltaW5nP2NtcGlkPUJCRDEwMDQyM19NT05FWVNUVUZGJnV0bV9tZWRpdW09ZW=
1haWwmdXRtX3NvdXJjZT1uZXdzbGV0dGVyJnV0bV90ZXJtPTIzMTAwNCZ1dG1fY2FtcGFpZ249b=
W9uZXlzdHVmZg/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB2334f9e4" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" ite=
mscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decora=
tion: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #0000=
00; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">art dealers</a> =
=E2=80=94 =E2=80=9Cif someone comes to you with an enormous sack of cash, o=
r crypto, or a wire transfer from North Korea,=C2=A0maybe ask some question=
s about where it came from and report it to the authorities.=E2=80=9D=C2=A0=
</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">On the other hand if you do crime and have sac=
ks of cash and take some cash out of a sack and go to a deli to get a sandw=
ich and pay cash, the deli will not report you to anyone. You can=E2=80=99t=
 really launder your money through sandwiches.=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">There is some intermediate zone between =E2=80=
=9Csandwiches=E2=80=9D and =E2=80=9CCentral Park South penthouses=E2=80=9D =
where, you know, you=C2=A0<em>could=C2=A0</em>be laundering money, or you c=
ould just carry around a lot of cash and want to spend it. It is a line-dra=
wing exercise, and <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click=
/32923785.285424/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZnQuY29tL2NvbnRlbnQvYzhkZDEzMjUtY2VjZC00MT=
JiLWExNDMtMWRiMDM0NzYxMzA4/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBf24df4dc" itemprop=3D"S=
toryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000=
; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom=
-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">somet=
imes the line moves</a>:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Singapore may subject luxury assets, including=
 cars, watches and handbags, to anti-money laundering controls and increase=
 scrutiny of single family offices as the Asian financial hub reels from a =
S$2.8bn (US$2bn) money-laundering scandal.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">In response to questions in parliament on Tues=
day about the probe, Singapore=E2=80=99s government said it would examine e=
xtending anti-money laundering requirements, such as tough know-your-custom=
er due diligence checks, to high-value assets including vehicles, handbags =
and alcohol. Such items are not currently regulated, unlike precious stones=
 or metals.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">If you have ill-gotten money, you might park i=
t in diamonds, so if you walk into a diamond dealer they will ask you =E2=
=80=9Cis this money ill-gotten?=E2=80=9D Or you might park it in, like, <a =
href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/32923785.285424/aHR0c=
HM6Ly9lbi53aWtpcGVkaWEub3JnL3dpa2kvUGFwcHlfVmFuX1dpbmtsZSUyN3NfRmFtaWx5X1Jl=
c2VydmU/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBe0fe7263" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=
=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: =
none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; bo=
rder-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">Pappy Van Winkle</a>.=C2=
=A0The liquor store will not=C2=A0<em>necessarily=C2=A0</em>ask you =E2=80=
=9Cis this money ill-gotten?=E2=80=9D before selling you a bottle, but mayb=
e they should.</p>
